                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote xml:id="d1">Decorative designs: harägs in black and red ff. 47r, 71r, 93r, 156r, 165v, 166r; late haräg-like designs in blue ink ff. 17v, 26v, 38v, 53r; late haräg-like design in pencil f. 108r; dotted lines in alternating black and red ff. 124v, 132v, 186r; dotted line in red f. 1r; line in black bars and read dots f. 108r; lines in black (and sometimes red) joined with stops ff. 8v, 73v, 92v, 140v, 178v, 184r.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
